 Ruger performs on stage during a show in Uganda. Photo: Ivan Kabuye/Kampala Sun It will be pomp and pageantry on Friday, March 25, as red-hot Nigerian artiste, Ruger, will thrill goers at the GoodLife N-tyce nightclub located on 1310 Karimu Kotun area of Victoria Island, Lagos. Maximum fun and relaxation is assured as other celebrities will throng the nightclub for the pull up party sponsored by top blended Scotch whisky Chivas Regal. The serene location, ambiance, music and calibre of guests at Good Life N-tyce will certainly put you in the mood for a time of relaxation and maximum fun.
