Chivas Regal and GoodLife N-tyce are associated with class and grandeur, reason why Ruger, one of Nigeria’s most highly sought-after music superstars, will be on hand to serenade you deep into the night and till the early hours of the morning. It is no debate that GoodLife N-tyce offers one of the best karaoke experiences in Lagos, and boasts of beautiful and comfortable lounges – outside and inside the venue. The meals are tastier and the service is top-notch by excellent attendants readily on hand to attend to clubbers. Ultimately, apart from leaving clubbers with unforgettable moments on Friday, the breath-taking photo booth leaves them with opportunities on the night to keep a tangible evidence of the they had for a long time. 